title: #89: NXIVM With The Truth Factory Cat
description: Welcome to another crazy episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode Sam and Ryan welcome from the Truth Factory, The Truth Cat, to explore  the bizarre world of Keith Raniere and the NXIVM cult!  Please enjoy and thank you for your support.
